  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6835.68 trading just below the GEX flip at 6839, dealers are currently in long gamma mode and likely buying this dip as spot approaches the 6835 support wall (+10.4B GEX). The massive positive gamma concentration between 6835-6850 creates a strong gravitational pull that should limit downside and attract price back toward the 6840-6850 zone where dealers will resume selling into strength. Key levels to watch: 6820 negative gamma wall as the critical support (dealers amplify moves below here) and 6850 max positive gamma as the upside magnet where dealer selling intensifies.\n\n**Bottom line:** expect the market to bounce back toward 6840-6850 with limited downside risk.",
